channel.title: Silab Item and Spawn help
channel.description: Ok, so i added the D Bow to my item list and changed the number so it was next after my last, but when i try to spawn it, it gives me a Small Fishing Net! What am i doing wrong? Im using Project16 V6. Also how do i change where my player starts out when they first login?

item.title: Silab Item and Spawn help
item.dc:creator: @nubsta nubsta
item.description:
@nubsta wrote:

are you using silab client? You change where your player starts by going to player.java. Search for “initial x and y coordinates of the player” and the part under it that says teleportToX and teleportToY change the coords after it to the x and y coords.

Read full topic
